ğŸ“‹ RESEARCH METHODOLOGY
For Each Section:
Identify Required Information

What facts/specifications are needed?
What level of detail is necessary?
What sources are authoritative?
Gather Information

Primary sources first (DTCC, SEC)
Secondary sources for context (industry publications)
Tertiary sources for background only
Validate & Cross-Reference

Verify facts from multiple sources when possible
Flag single-source claims (need verification)
Document assumptions clearly
Cite Properly

Footnotes with URLs for web sources
Document titles and dates for regulations
Industry contact: "Industry interview, Dec 2025 (anonymous)"
Update This Log

Record all sources consulted
Note what was found vs. what's still missing
Track validation status
